Package Project3

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Company
    An array-based container class that implements the employee database.
    Controller
    The controller is used to handle the interaction between the graphic user interface and the functions.
    Date
    This class implements a Date object with year, month, and day.
    Employee
    Defines the common data and operations for all employee type.
    Fulltime
    Includes specific data and operations to a full-time employee.
    Main
    The driver class to run project 3.
    Management
    Extends the Fulltime class and includes specific data and operations to a full-time employee with a management role.
    Parttime
    Extends the Employee class and includes specific data and operations to a part-time employee.
